Author: Gateway#3763
Content:
[telegram] <Regnar> The whole Komodo ecosystem is this way, almost all Komodo asset chains are runtime forks with Komodo, so updates and new features on Komodo can be pushed to different asset chains, and vice versa. 
Verus solved the nothing at stake problem and actually pushed their custom mining algorithm back to Komodo, which can now pass that to new asset chains that want it. Also Pirate, Komodo, and Verus, as well as over 40 other blockchains in Komodo updated to Sapling addresses all at once. These are huge benefits to building in the Komodo ecosystem (re @jason_1986: Awesome! Makes me more comfortable investing knowing there are strong links with Komodo team! :D)
